<s> This may not be perfectly stated, but its intent is not that obscure.  </s>
<s> A better way of putting it might be: "While we specify two SignatureMethod algorithms, one mandatory and one optional to implement, user specified algorithms may be used as SignatureMethod algorithms instead."  </s>
